{"id":15395,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/15395","type":2,"name":"戦国BASARA 劇場版 -The Last Party-","name_cn":"战国BASARA 剧场版 -The Last Party-","summary":"時は群雄割拠の戦国時代、\r\n覇王・豊臣秀吉の起こした動乱は終結した。だが、戦乱の世は未だ終わることなく、覇王の不在は新たな戦を日ノ本に呼ぶ……！\r\n一つは奥州に闇あり。伊達政宗の前に現れた修羅の如き凶王――名は石田三成。崇敬する主、秀吉を討った怨敵・政宗に抱く私怨が世にもたらすものとは何か。\r\n一つは戦場に光あり。武田と上杉の永き因縁に終止符が打たれようとした時に降り立った、槍を捨て己の拳のみを武器とする男――名は徳川家康。「絆」の力を持って天下統一を成すとする決意、その理想が、戦なき世を望む者たちに抱かせる思いとは何か。\r\nそして、関ヶ原に混沌あり。宿命を背負いし武将たちは全ての決着を着けるため、戦国の世に暗躍する影が誘いし決戦の地・関ヶ原へ――","eps":[{"id":545177,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545177","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-06-04","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"2011-06-04","air_weekday":6,"rating":{"total":228,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":1,"4":6,"5":17,"6":64,"7":89,"8":40,"9":6,"10":4},"score":6.7},"rank":2853,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/bc/bb/20914_fjkJl.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/bc/bb/20914_fjkJl.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/bc/bb/20914_fjkJl.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/bc/bb/20914_fjkJl.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/bc/bb/20914_fjkJl.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":140,"collect":347,"doing":4,"on_hold":16,"dropped":14},"crt":[{"id":218,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/218","name":"伊達政宗","name_cn":"伊达政宗","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/f9/88/218_crt_eAzaD.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/f9/88/218_crt_eAzaD.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/f9/88/218_crt_eAzaD.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f9/88/218_crt_eAzaD.jpg"},"comment":19,"collects":73,"info":{"name_cn":"伊达政宗","gender":"男","height":"160"},"actors":[{"id":4424,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/4424","name":"中井和哉","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/83/45/4424_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/83/45/4424_seiyu_anidb.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/83/45/4424_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/83/45